t=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533364\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wif1665702767979.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wif1665702767979.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wif1665702767979.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wif1665702767979\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n Triggers in Static Server Pages \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wif1665702767979__triggers_in_static_server_pages_75205\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Static server pages have non-interactive triggers. Only the field-level detail trigger for a Button widget is interactive.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wif1665702767979__p_d21602e1_d21603e1_d21604e1\">GOLD key combinations are not available because browsers do not support them.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wif1665702767979__p_d21605e1_d21606e1_d21607e1\">An empty exec operation contains an implicit <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement. In static server pages, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement is treated as a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webget</span> followed by a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> statement.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Triggers Available in Static Server Pages</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__1\">\n Level\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__2\">\n Available for Server Pages\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__1\">\n Component\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__2\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10541e1_d10542e1_d10543e1\">receiveMessage trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10544e1_d10545e1_d10546e1\">exec operation\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10547e1_d10548e1_d10549e1\">preActivate trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10550e1_d10551e1_d10552e1\">postActivate trigger\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__1\">\n Entity\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__2\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10553e1_d10554e1_d10555e1\">delete trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10556e1_d10557e1_d10558e1\">deleteUp trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10559e1_d10560e1_d10561e1\">lock trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10562e1_d10563e1_d10564e1\">error trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10565e1_d10566e1_d10567e1\">preDeserialize trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10568e1_d10569e1_d10570e1\">postDeserialize trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10571e1_d10572e1_d10573e1\">preSerialize trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10574e1_d10575e1_d10576e1\">postSerialize trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10577e1_d10578e1_d10579e1\">read trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10580e1_d10581e1_d10582e1\">write trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10583e1_d10584e1_d10585e1\">writeUp trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10586e1_d10587e1_d10588e1\">validate trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1\">validate trigger\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__1\">\n Field\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wif1665702767979__table_d2459e1_d2460e1_d2461e1__entry__2\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10592e1_d10593e1_d10594e1\">detail trigger <a href=\"#fntarg_1\" name=\"fnsrc_1\"><sup>1</sup></a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10595e1_d10596e1_d10597e1\">formatToDisplay trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10598e1_d10599e1_d10600e1\">formatFromDisplay trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10601e1_d10602e1_d10603e1\">formatToDbms trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1\">formatFromDbms trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10607e1_d10608e1_d10609e1\">error trigger\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wif1665702767979__li_d10610e1_d10611e1_d10612e1\">validate trigger\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wif1665702767979__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://learn.rocketsoftware.com/course/view.php?id=50\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Learn More\" class=\"image\" id=\"wif1665702767979__image_mxp_ql4_vdc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Learn_More_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fn\"><a href=\"#fnsrc_1\" name=\"fntarg_1\"><sup>1</sup></a>  Supported on the\n                              Button widget</div></article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yfu1665702863131.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Static Server Pages</a><p>Static Server Page (USP) components generate a complete web page every time they are activated. This makes them useful for relatively static web pages or a thin-client architecture in which all processing is done on the server. They can also be used for RESTful applications or file upload functionality.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcj1719477302864.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Triggers in Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>Dynamic server pages (DSPs) have system triggers that are executed on the server, and client-side web triggers that are executed in the browser.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533364\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533364\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Triggers in Static Server Pages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Triggers in Static Server Pages Static server pages have non-interactive triggers. Only the field-level detail trigger for a Button widget is interactive. GOLD key combinations are not available because browsers do not support them. An empty exec operation contains an implicit edit statement. In static server pages, the edit statement is treated as a webget followed by a webgen statement. Table 1. Triggers Available in Static Server Pages Level Available for Server Pages Component receiveMessage trigger exec operation preActivate trigger postActivate trigger Entity delete trigger deleteUp trigger lock trigger error trigger preDeserialize trigger postDeserialize trigger preSerialize trigger postSerialize trigger read trigger write trigger writeUp trigger validate trigger validate trigger Field detail trigger 1 formatToDisplay trigger formatFromDisplay trigger formatToDbms trigger formatFromDbms trigger error trigger validate trigger 1 Supported on the Button widget Related Links Static Server Pages Static Server Page (USP) components generate a complete web page every time they are activated. This makes them useful for relatively static web pages or a thin-client architecture in which all processing is done on the server. They can also be used for RESTful applications or file upload functionality. Triggers in Dynamic Server Pages Dynamic server pages (DSPs) have system triggers that are executed on the server, and client-side web triggers that are executed in the browser. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}